               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="15v">1v-15v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s36IHA">قران, Twenty ninth ǧuz’ (29/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>سورة الملك ثلاثون اىت (هكذا) مكيه \ بِسـمِ اللهِ الرّحْمَنِ الرّحِيم ,  تَبَارَكَ الذّيْ بِيَدِهِ المُلْكُ وَهْوَ عَلَىْ كُلِّ شَئٍ قَدِيْرُ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#15-15v">-15-15v</locus>وَإِذَا قِيْلَ لَهُمٌ أرْكَعُوْا لَا يَرْكَعُوْنَ , وَىْلُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلْمُكَذِّبِيْنَ فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيْثِ بَعْدَهُ يُؤْمِنُوْنَ<note>Hamza in the word "yawma'iḏin" is written on a yā' with dots.</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>67:1-77:50. Rubricated suras, red dots as verse markers. Eleven to fourteen lines a page. Words completed vertically line at the end of lines (ex. 3v, 6r, 12r). Extensions of words into the left margin. Artistic realization of final letter hā' (5v). Deletions. Catchwords written with a blue ball point pen on fol. 7v, 12v and 13v.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
